Brand: Diveblues.
Template type: Newsletter / welcome subscription.

Subject suggestion: Welcome to Diveblues
Preview text suggestion: Fresh scenes, easy carry, and a cooler way to move through your day.

Effects tested:
- One-image welcome hero using the approved Shopify Files URL.
- Personalized greeting with customer.first_name default fallback.
- Newsletter expectation-setting copy for new subscribers.
- Single primary CTA to the all-products collection.
- Reusable Diveblues footer/contact constants.
- Open tracking enabled.
- Dark-mode fallback using solid backgrounds and explicit text colors.

How to paste:
1. Open Shopify Email.
2. Add or edit a custom Liquid section.
3. Paste this whole template.
4. Send a test email.
5. Record results in outputs/diveblues/edm/templates/index.md.

Test checklist:
- Exactly one image renders.
- Gmail, Outlook, Apple Mail.
- Mobile viewport.
- Dark mode.
- Image-off rendering.
- CTA link.
- Support/social footer links.
- Physical mailing address.
- Unsubscribe link.
- Open tracking.
- File size under 50KB for this custom Liquid section.

Pending variable verification:
- all_products[handle] / product variables are not used.
- customer.accepts_marketing is not used.
